2. 处理数据集 - Oakland Crime Statistics 2011 to 2016¶

数据集分析 ： 这是加州Okaland市2011-2016年犯罪率相关的数据，主要文件有11-16六个csv格式数据组成，数据表中记录的属性有Agency \ Create Time \ Locatio \ Area Id \ Beat \ Priority \ Incident Type Id \ Incident Type Description \ Event Number \ Closed Time等，其中部分年份的数据记录中缺失Location属性。

In [4]:
for i in ["2012","2014"]:
    crime_data_dict[i].rename(columns={"Location 1":"Location"}, inplace = True)
    crime_data_dict[i].drop("Zip Codes",axis=1, inplace=True)
    crime_data_dict[i]["Location"] = crime_data_dict[i]["Location"].map(lambda Location : re.findall(r"\"address\": \"(.+?)\"", str(Location)))
    crime_data_dict[i]["Location"] = crime_data_dict[i]["Location"].map(lambda Location : ''.join(Location))

for i in ["2011","2012","2013","2014"]:
    crime_data_dict[i]["Area Id"].fillna("*")
    crime_data_dict[i]["Area Id"].apply("str")
    crime_data_dict[i]["Area Id"] = crime_data_dict[i]["Area Id"].map(lambda ID : "P" + str(ID)[:1])
    crime_data_dict[i]["Area Id"] = crime_data_dict[i]["Area Id"].replace("P*",np.NaN)
    crime_data_dict[i]["Area Id"] = crime_data_dict[i]["Area Id"].replace("Pn",np.NaN)
#     print(crime_data_dict[i])

for i in ["2011","2012","2013","2014","2015","2016"]:
#     print(crime_data_dict[i]["Area Id"])
    crime_data_dict[i].rename(columns={"Location ":"Location"}, inplace = True)
    crime_data_dict[i]["Location"] = crime_data_dict[i]["Location"].map(lambda Location : str(Location).strip()) 
    print(crime_data_dict[i].columns.size, end=",")
# print(crime_data_dict["2013"]["Location"])

数据可视化和摘要 :
标称属性: 其中大部分为标称数据，其主要的标称属性有Agency, Area Id, Beat, Location, Incident Type Id, Event Number
数值属性: 部分为数值属性，包括Create Time, Priority, Closed Time

对于标称数据进行分析如下：

  1. Agency : 所有的Agency属性都是"OP",故因此无需进行频度分析.
  2. Event Number ： 对于该属性每个记录是不同的，故意无需进行频度分析.
  3. Location 的属性种类过多, 亦作简化的数据的频度分析.
  4. Beats, Incident typea ID 的分析图如下:
  5. Priority属性类别少,可以作完整的直方图

Closed Time : 对于Closed Time而言则更加复杂一些，这四种方法分别时间如下：
A. 将缺失部分剔除
B. 用最高频率值来填补缺失值(时间取为平均结束时间)
C. 通过属性的相关关系来填补缺失值(根据结束时间 = 开始时间 + priority * A + B 进行回归拟合)
D. 通过数据对象之间的相似性来填补缺失值(根据该项与Incident Type Id项的相似性进行填补)

因为是时间数据，因而最终拟合与可视化的媒介都表现为持续时间。
同时 因为缺失值太少补全后影响太小 故仅仅对补充的值单独进行可视化。

A_con = A_end - A_start
A_con = A_con.map(lambda x: x/np.timedelta64(1,'m'))   # 时间持续时间

cltime_D = crime_data_merge.copy()["Closed Time"].reset_index(drop=True)
crtime_D = crime_data_merge.copy()["Create Time"].reset_index(drop=True)
priority_D = crime_data_merge.copy()["Priority"].reset_index(drop=True)
time_series = pd.DataFrame(list(zip(cltime_D , crtime_D , priority_D )),columns=["Closed Time" , "Create Time","Priority"])
time_series = time_series.reset_index(drop=True)

time_series_base = time_series.dropna()
time_series_drop_index = np.where(cltime_D.isnull().values==True)[0]
time_series_drop = pd.DataFrame(list(zip(crtime_D[time_series_drop_index] , cltime_D[time_series_drop_index] , priority_D[time_series_drop_index])),columns=["Closed Time" , "Create Time","Priority"])
base_start = time_series_base["Create Time"].map(lambda i : str(i)[:10] +'-' + str(i)[-12:-4])
base_start = pd.to_datetime(base_start ,format="%Y-%m-%d-%H:%M:%S")

base_end = time_series_base["Closed Time"].map(lambda i : str(i)[:10] +'-' + str(i)[-12:-4])
base_end = pd.to_datetime(base_end ,format="%Y-%m-%d-%H:%M:%S")

con_base = base_end - base_start
con_base = con_base.map(lambda x: x/np.timedelta64(1,'m'))  

model_crime = LinearRegression() 
model_crime.fit(time_series_base["Priority"].values.reshape(-1, 1), con_base.values.reshape(-1, 1)) 
print("拟合的表达式为：%.4f * x + (%.4f) + e " %(model_crime.coef_,model_crime.intercept_) ) 
con_fit = model_crime.predict(time_series_drop["Priority"].values.reshape(-1,1))
D_con = con_fit.reshape(-1)

3. 处理数据集 - Wine Reviews¶

数据集分析 ：
该数据集是对于葡萄酒的品鉴结果收集集,两个数据集中记载了130k与150k的葡萄酒品鉴评论,其中第二个数据集为作者后来重新爬取的结果，这次爬取中作者额外收集了每个评论的标题、年份、品酒者的姓名和品酒者的Twitter句柄，并解决了重复输入的问题，因此这里主要处理的是winemag-data-130k-v2.csv,另一个表仅作绘图时的参考。该数据集中属性包含有：country \ description \ designation \ points \ price \ province \ region_1 \ region_2 \ taster_name \ taster_twitter_handle \ title \ variety \ winery, 并给出了各个属性的描述。

缺省值的补充:
这里主要是实现对数值数据中缺省值的补充，而从上面已经得知主要缺失的是Price数据，因此下面使用上面提及到的四种方法对该缺省值进行填充。
A. 将缺失部分剔除
B. 用最高频率值来填补缺失值
C. 通过属性的相关关系来填补缺失值(非数值数据：忽略)
D. 通过数据对象之间的相似性来填补缺失值(相同地区的记录项的Id应当相同)

In [65]:
# price
price_A = price.dropna()

# print(price.value_counts(dropna = True)) #20.0      6940
price_B = price.fillna(20)

# 相关关系 price - points
pp_corr = pd.DataFrame(list(zip(points,price)),columns = ['points' , 'price'])
print("Price 与 Points相关性矩阵为：")
print(pp_corr.corr("spearman"))
# 拟合
pp_corr_drop = pp_corr.dropna()
model = LinearRegression() 
model.fit(pp_corr_drop["points"].values.reshape(-1, 1), pp_corr_drop["price"].values.reshape(-1, 1)) 
print("拟合的表达式为：%.4f * x + (%.4f) + e " %(model.coef_,model.intercept_) ) 
price_fit = model.predict(points.values.reshape(-1,1))
price_fit = price_fit.reshape(-1)
new_pp = pd.DataFrame(list(zip(price,price_fit)),columns = ['price' , 'price_fit'])
price_C = new_pp.price.combine_first(new_pp.price_fit)
print("C方法处理之后NaN个数 ：" , len(price_C) - len(price_C.dropna()))

# 相似性 (先找Varity 再找designation)
price_D = price.copy()
price_nan_index = np.where(price.isnull().values==True)[0]
variety_D = cdb_data_main["variety"]
designation_D = cdb_data_main["designation"]
for i in price_nan_index:
    variety_i = variety_D[i]
    designation_i = designation_D[i]
    v_poss = np.where(variety_D == variety_i)
    d_poss = np.where(designation_D == designation_i)
    and_index = list(set(v_poss[0]) & set(d_poss[0]) - set(list(price_nan_index)))
    if and_index != []:
        k = random.sample(and_index , 1)
        price_D[i] = price_D[k]
        continue
    v_index = list(set(v_poss[0]) - set(list(price_nan_index)))
    if v_index != []:
        k = random.sample(v_index , 1)
        price_D[i] = price_D[k]
        continue
    d_index = list(set(d_poss[0]) - set(list(price_nan_index)))
    if d_index != []:
        k = random.sample(d_index , 1)
        price_D[i] = price_D[k]
        continue
    ran_index = list(set(np.arange(0,len(price_D))) - set(list(price_nan_index)))
    k = random.sample(ran_index , 1)
    price_D[i] = price_D[k]
print("D方法处理之后NaN个数 ：" ,len(price_D) - len(price_D.dropna()))
